{
  "uid": "platform-overview",
  "title": "Lantern — Platform Overview",
  "tags": ["lantern", "ga"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "label": "Prometheus",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "options": []
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Control-plane up",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN" }, "1": { "text": "UP" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"lantern-control-plane\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "control-plane",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Gateway up",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 4,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN" }, "1": { "text": "UP" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"lantern-gateway\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "gateway",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Model-router up",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN" }, "1": { "text": "UP" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"lantern-model-router\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "model-router",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Control-plane /readyz",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "NOT READY" }, "1": { "text": "READY" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_success{job=\"lantern-control-plane-readyz\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "readyz",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Scheduler leader present",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "NO LEADER" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(lantern_scheduler_is_leader)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "leaders",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cron schedules overdue",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 20,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max(lantern_schedules_overdue)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "overdue",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Schedule RPC rate by result",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(lantern_scheduler_schedule_total[5m])) by (result)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{result}}",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Schedule error fraction",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(lantern_scheduler_schedule_errors_total[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(lantern_scheduler_schedule_total[5m])),0.001)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "error fraction",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Postgres connection saturation",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.7 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.9 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": []
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(pg_stat_database_numbackends{job=\"lantern-postgres-exporter\"}) / max(pg_settings_max_connections{job=\"lantern-postgres-exporter\"})",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "connection saturation",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "TODO — pending instrumentation",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Not emitted yet — do not trust as live\n\nThese metrics are **not exported** today. They exist only as **OTel traces**, not Prometheus series. Panels are intentionally omitted until instrumentation lands.\n\n| Metric | Intended panel |\n| --- | --- |\n| `lantern_http_requests_total` | control-plane 5xx error rate |\n| `lantern_runs_completed_total` | run failure rate |\n| `lantern_budget_denied_total` | API budget 402 rate |\n| `lantern_gateway_request_duration_seconds_bucket` | gateway p99 latency |\n| `lantern_model_router_request_duration_seconds_bucket` | model-router p99 latency |\n\n_When these land, replace this panel with the corresponding live panels._"
      }
    }
  ]
}
